-----

+* Usage

This is a Black Highlighter based theme, meaning you will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. To learn more, go [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|here]]].

**To import this theme, simply add the following to your page:**

> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:the-coalition-theme]]@@

@@ @@

+ Examples

[[div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:100px;"]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme:the-coalition-theme/GOClogo.png]]
[[div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:width:100px;;"]]
Coalition Logo
[[/div]]
[[/div]]

A horizontal rule can be created with 5 hyphens "@@-----@@" and extends across the whole page if it's not placed inside anything (eg a blockquote). The lines separating sections of this document are horizontal rules.

-----

Titles can be created by putting between one and six plus "+" at the start of the line

